---
---
<section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden" style="background-color: var(--color-dark);">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-20" style="background: url('https://images.pexels.com/photos/8134821/pexels-photo-8134821.jpeg?auto=compress&cs=tinysrgb&w=1600') center/cover no-repeat;"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(15,24,41,0.7) 0%, rgba(15,24,41,0.92) 100%);"></div>

  <div class="relative z-10 text-center px-6 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <img src="/logo.svg" alt="Dodo Works" class="h-12 mx-auto mb-8 opacity-90" />
    <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.4em] uppercase mb-6" style="color: var(--color-warm);">Web Design for Exterior</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white mb-6 leading-tight" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
      施工写真が映える、<br />
      <span style="color: var(--color-warm);">低価格・高品質</span>な<br />
      外構屋専門HP
    </h1>
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);">
      相場の1/10以下の価格で、施工事例が映えるプロ品質のHPを。<br />
      外構業界専門のエンジニアが制作します。
    </p>
    <a
      href="#contact"
      class="inline-block px-10 py-4 text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest transition-all duration-200 hover:brightness-110 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5"
      style="background-color: var(--color-warm); color: white;"
    >
      無料相談・お問い合わせ
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
